            <div class="content-text">
                <div class="table-responsive-wrapper">
                <table>
                    <thead><tr><th>Service</th><th>What We Do</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>Pre-Setup Structuring Memo</td><td>Two-week jurisdiction and entity review covering UK Ltd vs Singapore Pte Ltd vs US Delaware C-Corp vs UAE Free Zone. Maps GAAR, POEM, MLI PPT, India-UK DTAA, ECCT identity verification and the FEMA OI route for the specific use case.</td></tr>
