                        <tr><td>UK Bank Account Opening and Payment Processor Setup</td><td>Coordination with Wise Business, Revolut Business, Tide or Mettle (challenger banks - typical 1-2 weeks for foreign founders); HSBC, Barclays or NatWest (traditional - typically 4-6 weeks with in-person UK visit required); Stripe / GoCardless / Wise Multi-currency setup.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>India-UK DTAA and MLI PPT Positioning</td><td>TRC application from HMRC, beneficial ownership memo, treaty claim documentation for royalty, interest and dividend flows under the India-UK DTAA (as modified by 2012 Protocol and MLI) and PPT defence memo aligned with CBDT Circular 01/2025.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Ongoing Annual Compliance Pack</td><td>Companies House Confirmation Statement (annually; GBP 50 digital from 1 Feb 2026), Annual Accounts within 9 months of FY end, CT600 to HMRC within 12 months of period end, CT payment 9 months + 1 day after period end, VAT returns where registered, India APR by 31 December and Indian tax positions where applicable.</td></tr>

